      <title>茅台将失去中国最大股票的头衔，让位于工商银行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/moutai-set-to-lose-crown-as-china-s-biggest-stock-to-icbc</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于批发价格暴跌，贵州茅台股份有限公司似乎即将失去中国最有价值境内股票的地位，而中国工商银行股份有限公司将成为其竞争对手。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/moutai-set-to-lose-crown-as-china-s-biggest-stock-to-icbc</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 00:15:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>库存下降刺激看涨情绪，油价有望录得周涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-june-21</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国库存水平意外下降，加之产品需求强劲的迹象，油价有望自 4 月初以来首次连续两周上涨，这表明美国这一全球最大消费国的状况良好。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-june-21</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 23:23:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
